title: ArtistX Linux
description:
ARTISTX OS Linux

ArtistX 1.5 is a linux os with all multimedia and audio video tools(2D and 3D) for editing and creating audio and video files with ease. A tool for video Encoder, video customization, audio creation and many more.... Download and enjoy>>...



It can be used as live medium as well as installed version, can be run from DVD/Usb as Live and installed as normal OS as on HDD....
